Super Eagles Player,Kenneth Omeruo has supported his wife against former Eagles Captain,Austin JJ Okocha. On his Insta-story, Omeuro shared a photo of himself and wrote;
Block the noise (JJ and Nigerians criticizing his wife)
uoStay humble,Stay focused,Pray,Work harder,
And of course LOVE (Love in capitals to indicate he is with his wife?)
Recall his wife of only few months had taken to IG to call Okocha a mad man, shortly after he criticized her husband on Super Sports.
